Otu onye katara ahụ n'imepụta ejije na Nollywood bụ Moses Ebere, anwụọla.
Dịka ogbo ya bụ Sunny Mac Don, si gwa BBC Igbo n'ekwentị, Ebere, onye nwe ụlọọrụ mmepụta ihe ejije  a kpọrọ, 'Aim and See Entertainment', nwụrụ abalị abụọ gara aga nke bụ ụbọchị Tuzde.
Ihe ndị ị maghị maka Sam Obiago, onye ejije Nollywood a ma ama lara mmụọ
